 network 12.12.12.0 0.0.0.255 area 0
!
ip forward-protocol nd
!

no ip http server
no ip http secure-server
ip route 3.3.3.3 255.255.255.255 Tunnel1
!
!
line con 0
 logging synchronous
!
end
